Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.20,0:01:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,创造我朝的时候终于到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.14,0:01:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太师傅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.84,0:02:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.48,0:02:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太师傅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.38,0:02:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二十一话\N恶梦碎灭！\N雷十太之野望完结篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真惨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.18,0:02:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.78,0:03:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畜生！竟有这么多的枪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.25,0:03:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,革命开国终究本无谋之举
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.55,0:03:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死 本来就已觉悟 武士之精魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.32,0:03:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此刻将从日本神国\N永远地消失而去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.39,0:03:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹤左大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.66,0:03:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就大家同归于尽吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.96,0:04:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.57,0:04:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！不论敌人还是同志\N不要再互相残杀了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.14,0:04:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无谓的流血一滴也不准再流！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.51,0:04:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么东西！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.32,0:04:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下要与石动雷十太决斗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.79,0:04:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到分出胜败为止…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪一方面都不许攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.03,0:04:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木村先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照着绯村的话做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.70,0:04:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令他们停止攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么！…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.70,0:05:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是…绯村剑心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.47,0:05:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！停止攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.48,0:05:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在暂时休战！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.31,0:05:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真古流也把剑收起来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.55,0:05:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.82,0:05:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.82,0:05:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师傅！雷十太师傅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.53,0:05:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 我的脚被打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.44,0:05:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊 好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.41,0:05:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你！你是想绑架我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.22,0:05:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对！对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.15,0:05:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是被雇用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.62,0:05:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雷十太！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.89,0:05:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他拿钱请我们偷袭你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.26,0:05:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我师傅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.90,0:05:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是雷十太导的戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.43,0:06:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙为了卖恩情给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.64,0:06:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说谎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.57,0:06:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的！我们也被骗了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.31,0:06:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.71,0:06:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时偷袭你的人全被他给砍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师…师傅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师傅…我不会相信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.73,0:06:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直当您是我父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.21,0:06:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.58,0:06:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小由！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.78,0:06:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀斋…原来你还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.49,0:06:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让这次的战斗\N牺牲更多的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.29,0:07:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来此与你一决死活\N结束此事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.06,0:07:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.96,0:07:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们创立新王国\N的战斗没有你插手的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.34,0:07:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.60,0:07:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.78,0:07:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀斋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.94,0:07:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这位被歌颂为至强的志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一天等了很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.52,0:07:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我送你上西天的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.08,0:07:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我国最古的秘剑…饭纲秘剑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.40,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家 退开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.82,0:08:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是拔刀斋 让你侥幸躲过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 下一招你逃得了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.19,0:08:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.80,0:08:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太师傅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心他是我的救命人恩人呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.20,0:08:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他和师傅一样是位勇敢的剑豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.70,0:08:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国家大事我是不太懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 大家有话慢慢说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定能和师傅和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.45,0:09:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.68,0:09:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不让！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.95,0:09:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我求求您 请您听我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.22,0:09:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些话说了也没用的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.12,0:09:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的真面目\N你还认不太清楚吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.02,0:09:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！我师傅他会懂的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小由！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.08,0:09:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.98,0:09:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真过份…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.52,0:09:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师…师傅…您…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.36,0:09:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你！他是你的徒弟呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然对他 这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.07,0:09:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然 你的目的\N是小由的土地和财产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.74,0:10:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了建立自己的王国\N你只是在利用小由！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.41,0:10:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你说谎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.31,0:10:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说 我是他的徒弟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种蝼蚁之辈\N已无利用余地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.06,0:10:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想死的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.66,0:10:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以帮你早日超生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.73,0:10:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我这把你最心仪的剑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.64,0:10:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个卑鄙的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.87,0:10:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种卑鄙的小人\N还说什么武士魂 革命建国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.75,0:10:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎是多么地尊敬你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.98,0:10:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该最清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.99,0:10:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.96,0:10:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你将无数的剑客变成恶魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.03,0:11:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把纯洁无垢的少年的心\N作为你愚弄的对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.74,0:11:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这这种人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.94,0:11:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你尝尝地狱的滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.43,0:11:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.76,0:11:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你带由太郎\N到花小姐的家里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.20,0:11:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽快帮他疗伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.07,0:11:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之 你也去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.67,0:11:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这附近尚有人在打斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.34,0:11:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你保护薰小姐和由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.21,0:11:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.58,0:11:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦 你也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.02,0:11:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让我代替由太郎\N为这个家伙送终
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.42,0:12:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 你一定要打倒他喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.39,0:12:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 你退下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你倒挺有自信嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.00,0:12:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让由太郎白白地受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.57,0:12:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从他的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.91,0:12:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已看清你的剑招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.98,0:12:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤迸裂却不流血的伤口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.48,0:12:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此乃是利用空气的断层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.55,0:12:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,产生的真空波所造成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓“镰鼬”旋风的原理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.69,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘剑饭纲绝技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下将以我的剑降服你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你看透了我的剑招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.99,0:12:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就真能打倒我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.96,0:12:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斩人剑拔刀斋\N传说中的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我的剑打倒你的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.63,0:12:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是我迎接黎明之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.70,0:12:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好用你的尸体 来摆庆功宴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.27,0:12:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘剑 穿地饭纲剑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.60,0:13:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,击中了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了拔刀斋了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.25,0:13:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再怎么出招也无济于事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.09,0:13:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你的饭纲剑\N只能靠地面传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.49,0:13:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲开它实在太容易了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.83,0:13:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然只用穿地饭纲剑\N是无法打倒拔刀斋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.06,0:13:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么！飞空饭纲剑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.17,0:13:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饭纲剑竟然也能直接飞射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逮到你了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.65,0:14:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.65,0:14:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是饭纲剑法\N终结杀人剑法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很高兴吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.16,0:14:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一点小伤 就那么高兴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.59,0:14:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子 死不服输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.30,0:14:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我手上留下这丑恶的伤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子！死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.11,0:15:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.48,0:15:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把饭纲剑法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.88,0:15:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.52,0:15:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,土龙闪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.43,0:15:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙槌闪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫人难以置信…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他斩了饭纲剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.69,0:15:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们…原来只是在做白日梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.84,0:16:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求死容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活下去才真正需要勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.71,0:16:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.18,0:16:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了对我所夺的生命赎罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.25,0:16:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.33,0:16:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？你说绯村大人胜了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.50,0:16:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争终于结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.77,0:16:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不必死就解决了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.54,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟杀了怪物般的雷十太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.61,0:16:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.38,0:16:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又制造了传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.25,0:16:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是伤了右手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.02,0:16:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命别无大碍…可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.62,0:16:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.86,0:17:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右手臂的神经\N和筋肉都全被切断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.93,0:17:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也无能为力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.27,0:17:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜   可能 \N他再也无法练剑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.31,0:17:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他衷心地热爱剑术\N竟然 却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.05,0:17:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畜生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.85,0:17:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畜生…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.19,0:17:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 由太郎现在呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.23,0:17:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件事之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说这一个月都关在房间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.17,0:17:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不但再也不能练剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.24,0:17:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还被敬如父亲的雷十太背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.44,0:17:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他应是人生的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.61,0:17:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全地被否定掉般的心境吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.64,0:17:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰！我们神谷活心流\N乃是助人的剑道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.65,0:18:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有办法可以帮助他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真窝囊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.12,0:18:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在这种时候\N却一点也帮不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.79,0:18:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.96,0:18:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直像在守夜一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.63,0:18:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你干嘛嬉皮笑脸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.00,0:18:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话题中的由太郎有信来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.30,0:18:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.14,0:18:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神谷道场的各位 近来好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.97,0:18:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,种种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多受您们的照应\N我决定要和我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.18,0:18:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.18,0:18:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在德国的叔父一起住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德国？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.28,0:18:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想忘掉\N在日本发生的所有事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.39,0:18:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能…再也不会回来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.39,0:18:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.77,0:18:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少爷的叔父大人在德国学医
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.34,0:18:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若以德国医学水准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.04,0:19:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少爷的手能医好也说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.78,0:19:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小由的手一定会医好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.52,0:19:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果医好了 一定要回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.92,0:19:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神谷道场随时欢迎你回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小由…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.83,0:19:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久船就要开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.87,0:19:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们专程来送行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.94,0:19:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 祝大家身体健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.04,0:19:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就此失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.61,0:19:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少爷 该走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.64,0:19:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小由！你要提起精神哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.79,0:19:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.63,0:19:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.73,0:19:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样被吓跑了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.36,0:19:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.63,0:19:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被雷十太欺骗是那么痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.70,0:20:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就应该变得比雷十太强\N来克服这痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.87,0:20:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太那家伙\N也没什么了不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.68,0:20:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得超越\N你梦中的雷十太才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.82,0:20:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你做不到的话\N你将一生做只丧家犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.99,0:20:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！我不出声…\N你说谁是丧家犬啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.96,0:20:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会放弃练剑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.56,0:20:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放弃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有左手在！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的话 左手就足够了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.77,0:20:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.17,0:20:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等着！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.31,0:20:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要打倒你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.01,0:20:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛！试看看呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这初生茅庐的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.51,0:20:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 你这浑蛋 皮痒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.71,0:20:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来…已经没有问题了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.25,0:20:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样\N冢山由太郎出发去了德国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.43,0:20:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.43,0:21:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的胜负还没完喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.37,0:21:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明神祢彦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.37,0:21:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我若是回来 首先要打倒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.25,0:21:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们神谷道场\N又多加了一块名牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.02,0:21:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我宝贵的门下徒弟\N冢山由太郎的名牌
